code>rect()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/resetTransform\"><code>resetTransform()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/restore\"><code>restore()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/rotate\"><code>rotate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/save\"><code>save()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/scale\"><code>scale()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/scrollPathIntoView\"><code>scrollPathIntoView()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/setLineDash\"><code>setLineDash()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/setTransform\"><code>setTransform()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/stroke\"><code>stroke()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/strokeRect\"><code>strokeRect()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/strokeText\"><code>strokeText()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/transform\"><code>transform()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/translate\"><code>translate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Canvas 2D API 的 <code><strong>CanvasRenderingContext2D</strong></code><strong><code>.clearRect()</code></strong> 方法可以設定指定矩形（經由坐標 <em>(x, y)</em> 及大小 <em>(width, height)</em>）範圍內的所有像素為透明，清除所有先前繪製的內容。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"語法","title":"語法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">void <var><em>ctx</em>.clearRect(x, y, width, height);</var>\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"參數","title":"參數","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"x\"><code>x</code></dt>\n <dd>The x axis of the coordinate for the rectangle starting point.</dd>\n <dt id=\"y\"><code>y</code></dt>\n <dd>The y axis of the coordinate for the rectangle starting point.</dd>\n <dt id=\"width\"><code>width</code></dt>\n <dd>The rectangle's width.</dd>\n <dt id=\"height\"><code>height</code></dt>\n <dd>The rectangle's height.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"usage_notes","title":"Usage notes","isH3":false,"content":"<p>A common problem with <code>clearRect</code> is that it may appear it does not work when not <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Drawing_shapes#drawing_paths\">using paths properly</a>. Don't forget to call <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/beginPath\"><code>beginPath()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> before starting to draw the new frame after calling <code>clearRect</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"範例","title":"範例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"using_the_clearrect_method","title":"Using the <code>clearRect</code> method","isH3":true,"content":"<p>This is just a simple code snippet which uses the <code>clearRect</code> method.</p>\n\n<h4 id=\"html\">HTML</h4>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>canvas</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>canvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>canvas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<h4 id=\"javascript\">JavaScript</h4>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js; highlight:[11] notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> canvas <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'canvas'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> ctx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> canvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getContext</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'2d'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">beginPath</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">moveTo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">20</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">20</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">lineTo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">200</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">20</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">lineTo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">120</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">120</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">closePath</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// draws last line of the triangle</span>\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">stroke</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">clearRect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// clear the whole canvas</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// ctx.clearRect(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height);</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Edit the code below and see your changes update live in the canvas:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Playable code sample\" id=\"frame_playable_code\" width=\"700\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/clearRect/_sample_.playable_code.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>","titleAsText":"Using the clearRect method"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"規範","id":"規範","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/canvas.html#dom-context-2d-clearrect-dev","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.CanvasRenderingContext2D.clearRect"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"瀏覽器相容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.CanvasRenderingContext2D.clearRect","dataURL":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/clearRect/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"參見","title":"參見","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>The interface defining it, <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/fillRect\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D.fillRect()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/strokeRect\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D.strokeRect()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"語法","id":"語法"},{"text":"Usage notes","id":"usage_notes"},{"text":"範例","id":"範例"},{"text":"規範","id":"規範"},{"text":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"瀏覽器相容性"},{"text":"參見","id":"參見"}],"summary":"Canvas 2D API 的 CanvasRenderingContext2D.clearRect() 方法可以設定指定矩形（經由坐標 (x, y) 及大小 (width, height)）範圍內的所有像素為透明，清除所有先前繪製的內容。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.clearRect()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.clearRect()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.clearRect()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.clearRect()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.clearRect()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.clearRect()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.clearRect()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/api/canvasrenderingcontext2d/clearrect","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/web/api/canvasrenderingcontext2d/clearrect/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web","title":"給開發者的網頁技術文件"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D","title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/clearRect","title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.clearRect()"}],"pageTitle":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.clearRect() - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}